snippet.title: I Like Walking Very Much - Playthrough (textless 2D walking-simulator)
snippet.description:
-- I Like Walking Very Much - Playthrough (textless 2D walking-simulator) --
I Like Walking Very Much is a textless 2D walking-simulator. Play as a strange spider who loves walking very much.

The game will be end in 30 minutes more or less, very easy control, There are no hidden items or achievements. It's very tiny game.

https://camel504.itch.io/ilwvm

Updated         Dec 05, 2016
Published Apr 02, 2016
Status         Released
Platforms Windows, macOS
Author         camel504
Genre         Adventure
Tags         2D, spider, textless, Walking simulator
